-- Barroso Backs Latvia’s Euro Goal, Baltic Nation’s President Says
-- B y   A a r o n   E g l i t i s
-- 2012-11-13T08:08:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-13/barroso-backs-latvia-s-euro-goal-baltic-nation-s-president-says.html
European Commission President  Jose Barroso  supports Latvia’s ambitions to adopt the euro in 2014,
the Baltic nation’s President Andris Berzins said in an e-mailed
statement after a meeting between the two yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Eglitis in Riga at 
 aeglitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at   bpenz@bloomberg.net  